對住鬼佬就縮 對住靚女就偷拍既垃圾香港警察"},{"pid":"3988043fbf7bbc582d15fbbc2aedfb37144a609a","tid":382023,"uid":116045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人唔做走去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為錢出賣靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n無錢味要餓死? 係味你養我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港就係俾你呢種奴隸壞彎哂<br />\n<br />\n大把方法搵到錢 肯做功課可以學投資 或者紮鐵地盤做真漢子 衰d咪做住文職再進修自己學一技之長 我識人學西餅做到買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就揀去做政府隻看門狗 仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢種垃圾思想入去Force俾班大sir洗腦就岩</blockquote><br />\n巴打做咩工"},{"pid":"f620b96f236bf370cbeeb8a1ac27ba2b1f111e84","tid":382023,"uid":133514,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人唔做走去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為錢出賣靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n無錢味要餓死? 係味你養我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港就係俾你呢種奴隸壞彎哂<br />\n<br />\n大把方法搵到錢 肯做功課可以學投資 或者紮鐵地盤做真漢子 衰d咪做住文職再進修自己學一技之長 我識人學西餅做到買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就揀去做政府隻看門狗 仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢種垃圾思想入去Force俾班大sir洗腦就人岩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係冇， 文員仔得萬幾 幾時先二萬<br />\n警察一出黎就 二皮 好運既有升 沙展<br />\n四皮 都黎 仲未計褔利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c640d8f29d430be478b0260f964e6fdb12749df1","tid":382023,"uid":609,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有人唔做走去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為錢出賣靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n無錢味要餓死? 係味你養我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港就係俾你呢種奴隸壞彎哂<br />\n<br />\n大把方法搵到錢 肯做功課可以學投資 或者紮鐵地盤做真漢子 衰d咪做住文職再進修自己學一技之長 我識人學西餅做到買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你就揀去做政府隻看門狗 仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢種垃圾思想入去Force俾班大sir洗腦就岩</blockquote><br />\n巴打做咩工</blockquote><br />\n我之前專科 依家都叫搵到三皮幾 而且工作係幫人 有意義<br />\n<br />\n身邊黑警中同 個撚個蛇王就叻 日日屌市民同埋諗去邊飲飲食食 完全唔似一個有學識既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個格同城管 公安好似<br />\n<br />\n當然佢地會覺得自己係人上人 尤其班幫辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我眼中 呢班人只係社會寄生蟲"},{"pid":"ae7f94d189e277d0afb975ee0611dd3da0d525e4","tid":382023,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2