ces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢種垃圾思想入去Force俾班大sir洗腦就人岩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係冇， 文員仔得萬幾 幾時先二萬<br />\n警察一出黎就 二皮 好運既有升 沙展<br />\n四皮 都黎 仲未計褔利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你上去投共搵仲多<br />\n<br />\n再唔係你做鴨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反正都係出賣人格同靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我做會計狗都有三皮既<br />\n<br />\n不過係咁 OT 囉<br />\n<br />\n我就唔信如果入到 PI 真係咁多人<br />\n咁有大志話唔做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲人葡萄pi有40k姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f95ee5ea847f51f7f958a272e4fe18c86c4e03","tid":382023,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警務人員薪級表第3點 (每月22,410元) 至警務人員薪級表第15點 (每月32,045元) (註 1)<br />\n<br />\n截止申請日期(日/月/年) :\t全年均接受申請<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n有冇現職巴打可以講兩句，有咩技巧咁。我係絲，怕過唔到體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 有無study group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e599a0ed43042543b227798c69060dac5bf3d9b","tid":382023,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> gogogo Pi 50k都黎緊啦 屌你<br />\n又有宿舍 又有🔫 玩曬啦"},{"pid":"2b04795273d8522d6cb29bd1486f82488495a157","tid":382023,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"認真出面真係咁多工做5、6年有3、4皮咩"},{"pid":"66c6080b4304d8cdcbbc3136469c8c17465e05d7","tid":382023,"uid":133514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真出面真係咁多工做5、6年有3、4皮咩</blockquote><br />\n味就係 如果唔係專私 真係無咩可能"},{"pid":"43d9273eab6be83d0d2197ed578f800f1eb34100","tid":382023,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci